## **What is Stellar?**
Stellar, or Stellar Lumens, is an open source, decentralized protocol for digital currency to fiat money low-cost transfers which allows cross-border transactions between any pair of currencies. The Stellar protocol is supported by a Delaware nonprofit corporation, the Stellar Development Foundation.

## **Data Description**
This dataset provides the history of daily prices of Stellar cryptocurrency. All the column descriptions are provided. Currency is USD.
